---
layout: base.njk
title: "Boutique E-commerce Shopify | Hariss Web — Sur-mesure pour professionnels"
description: "Création de boutiques Shopify sur-mesure pour grossistes et commerçants B2B. À partir de 990 € — premier échange offert."

hero_label: "( Offre e-commerce )"
hero_line1: "Vos clients"
hero_line2: "commandent en ligne."
hero_description: "Vous vendez en gros ou au détail — je construis la boutique Shopify qui fait le travail à votre place."
hero_cta: "Premier échange offert"

why_label: "( Pourquoi Shopify )"
why_title: "La plateforme"
why_title_italic: "qui tient la route."
why_intro: "Pas de compromis sur la fiabilité. Shopify, c'est la plateforme de confiance de millions de commerçants — et une interface que vos équipes maîtrisent en quelques heures."
why_points:
  - title: "Autonomie totale"
    description: "Vos équipes gèrent les produits, les stocks et les commandes sans jamais dépendre de moi. Interface simple, formation incluse."
  - title: "Fiabilité éprouvée"
    description: "Shopify gère l'hébergement, la sécurité et les mises à jour. Zéro maintenance technique de votre côté."
  - title: "Évolutif par nature"
    description: "Commencez simple. Ajoutez des fonctionnalités au fur et à mesure que votre activité grandit — sans tout reconstruire."

offer_label: "( L'offre )"
offer_title: "Boutique Shopify"
offer_title_italic: "sur-mesure."
offer_price: "990"
offer_subtitle: "À partir de — sur devis"
offer_description: "Chaque boutique est construite pour votre contexte précis : votre catalogue, vos clients, votre façon de travailler. Le prix réel dépend du périmètre — discutons-en."
offer_includes:
  - "Boutique Shopify configurée de A à Z"
  - "Catalogue produits & catégories"
  - "Paiement en ligne sécurisé"
  - "Thème personnalisé à votre image"
  - "Formation à la prise en main"
  - "Support au lancement"
offer_cta: "Premier échange offert — Demander un devis"

launch_label: "( Offre de lancement )"
launch_title: "2 places"
launch_title_italic: "disponibles."
launch_description: "Je construis mon portfolio e-commerce. Je recherche 2 commerçants partenaires pour des boutiques à tarif de lancement — en échange d'un retour d'expérience et d'une présence dans mon book."
launch_cta: "Je suis intéressé"

cta_label: "( On travaille ensemble ? )"
cta_title: "Un projet"
cta_title_italic: "en tête ?"
cta_description: "30 minutes d'échange, c'est gratuit. On fait le point sur votre besoin et je vous dis concrètement ce que je peux faire pour vous."
cta_button: "Démarrer la conversation"
---

<!-- =============================================
     HERO
     ============================================= -->
<section class="relative min-h-[100svh] flex items-end pb-24 px-6 md:px-12 grid-lines overflow-hidden w-full pt-32">

    <div class="w-full relative z-10 max-w-full">
        <p class="font-inter text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold mb-6 md:mb-8 reveal-text">
            <span class="line block">{{ hero_label }}</span>
        </p>

        <h1 class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="text-[13vw] md:text-[11vw] lg:text-[9vw] font-syne font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter text-white reveal-text block">
                <span class="line block">{{ hero_line1 }}</span>
            </span>
            <span class="text-[10vw] md:text-[8vw] lg:text-[6vw] font-syne font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter text-white reveal-text -mt-1 md:-mt-4 flex flex-row items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-0 lg:gap-6 flex-wrap">
                <span class="line block font-serif italic text-accent normal-case tracking-normal shrink-0">{{ hero_line2 }}</span>
            </span>
        </h1>

        <div class="mt-16 md:mt-20 flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-start lg:items-end gap-12 w-full">
            <div class="max-w-md reveal-text">
                <p class="font-inter text-gray-400 font-light text-base md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
                    <span class="line block">{{ hero_description }}</span>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal-text">
                <div class="line">
                    <a href="/contact/" class="btn-magnetic cursor-hover magnetic" data-magnetic-strength="50">
                        <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3">
                            {{ hero_cta }}
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-12 right-12 hidden md:flex items-center gap-4 origin-right rotate-90 opacity-50">
        <span class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.4em] text-white">Scroll</span>
        <div class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-white"></div>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- =============================================
     POURQUOI SHOPIFY
     ============================================= -->
<section class="relative py-32 md:py-40 px-6 md:px-12 bg-white text-black overflow-hidden w-full">

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl relative z-10">

        <div class="reveal-text mb-4">
            <p class="font-inter text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-400 font-bold">
                <span class="line block">{{ why_label }}</span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between gap-8 mb-20 md:mb-28">
            <h2 class="font-syne text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter reveal-text">
                <span class="line block">{{ why_title }}</span>
                <span class="line block font-serif italic font-normal normal-case tracking-normal text-black/30">{{ why_title_italic }}</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="font-inter text-gray-500 font-light text-base md:text-lg max-w-sm reveal-text">
                <span class="line block">{{ why_intro }}</span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 border-y border-black/10">
            {% for point in why_points %}
            <div class="{% if not loop.last %}border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r{% endif %} border-black/10 p-8 md:p-10 reveal-text">
                <p class="font-syne text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black/10 tracking-tighter mb-6">
                    <span class="line block">0{{ loop.index }}</span>
                </p>
                <h3 class="font-syne text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-black mb-4">
                    <span class="line block">{{ point.title }}</span>
                </h3>
                <p class="font-inter text-sm md:text-base text-gray-500 font-light leading-relaxed">
                    <span class="line block">{{ point.description }}</span>
                </p>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- =============================================
     L'OFFRE
     ============================================= -->
<section class="relative py-32 md:py-40 px-6 md:px-12 bg-pitch text-white overflow-hidden w-full grid-lines">

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl relative z-10">

        <div class="reveal-text mb-4">
            <p class="font-inter text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-accent font-bold">
                <span class="line block">{{ offer_label }}</span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-syne text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter mb-16 md:mb-24 text-white reveal-text">
            <span class="line block">{{ offer_title }}</span>
            <span class="line block font-serif italic font-normal normal-case tracking-normal text-white/30">{{ offer_title_italic }}</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start border-t border-white/10 pt-16">

            <!-- Prix -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-4 reveal-text">
                <p class="font-inter text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">
                    <span class="line block">{{ offer_subtitle }}</span>
                </p>
                <p class="font-syne text-7xl md:text-8xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter">
                    <span class="line block">{{ offer_price }}<span class="text-4xl">€</span></span>
                </p>
                <p class="font-serif italic text-gray-500 mt-4 text-lg">
                    <span class="line block">Sur devis — gratuit</span>
                </p>
                <div class="mt-10 reveal-text">
                    <a href="/contact/" class="btn-magnetic cursor-hover magnetic" data-magnetic-strength="50">
                        <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3">
                            {{ offer_cta }}
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Ce qui est inclus + description -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-7 lg:col-start-6">
                <p class="font-inter text-gray-400 font-light text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 reveal-text">
                    <span class="line block">{{ offer_description }}</span>
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-0 reveal-text">
                    {% for item in offer_includes %}
                    <li class="line flex items-center gap-4 py-4 border-b border-white/5">
                        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-accent rounded-full flex-shrink-0"></span>
                        <span class="font-inter text-sm md:text-base text-gray-300">{{ item }}</span>
                    </li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- =============================================
     OFFRE DE LANCEMENT
     ============================================= -->
<section class="relative py-32 md:py-40 px-6 md:px-12 bg-white text-black overflow-hidden w-full">

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl relative z-10">

        <div class="reveal-text mb-4">
            <p class="font-inter text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-gray-400 font-bold">
                <span class="line block">{{ launch_label }}</span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">

            <div class="lg:col-span-6">
                <h2 class="font-syne text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6 reveal-text">
                    <span class="line block">{{ launch_title }}</span>
                    <span class="line block font-serif italic font-normal normal-case tracking-normal text-black/20">{{ launch_title_italic }}</span>
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="lg:col-span-6">
                <p class="font-inter text-gray-500 font-light text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 reveal-text">
                    <span class="line block">{{ launch_description }}</span>
                </p>
                <div class="reveal-text">
                    <a href="/contact/"
                        class="line group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border border-black/20 text-xs font-syne uppercase tracking-wider text-black overflow-hidden cursor-hover magnetic rounded-full hover:border-accent transition-colors duration-500"
                        data-magnetic-strength="40">
                        <span class="relative z-10 transition-colors group-hover:text-white font-bold flex items-center gap-3">
                            {{ launch_cta }}
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-accent translate-y-[101%] group-hover:translate-y-[0%] transition-transform duration-500 ease-out z-0"></div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- =============================================
     CTA FINAL
     ============================================= -->
<section class="relative py-32 md:py-40 px-6 md:px-12 bg-pitch text-white overflow-hidden w-full">

    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl relative z-10 text-center">

        <div class="reveal-text mb-4">
            <p class="font-inter text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-accent font-bold">
                <span class="line block">{{ cta_label }}</span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-syne text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6 text-white reveal-text">
            <span class="line block">{{ cta_title }}</span>
            <span class="line block font-serif italic font-normal normal-case tracking-normal text-white/30">{{ cta_title_italic }}</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="font-inter text-gray-400 font-light text-lg md:text-xl max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed reveal-text">
            <span class="line block">{{ cta_description }}</span>
        </p>

        <div class="reveal-text">
            <a href="/contact/" class="btn-magnetic cursor-hover magnetic line" data-magnetic-strength="50">
                <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3">
                    {{ cta_button }}
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
                    </svg>
                </span>
            </a>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Decorative vertical text -->
    <div class="absolute top-64 right-12 hidden md:flex items-center gap-4 origin-right rotate-90 opacity-20 text-white">
        <span class="text-[1.2rem] uppercase font-bold tracking-[0.4em]">Shopify</span>
        <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-white"></div>
    </div>
</section>
